{"type":"message","id":"b057e9e9","parentId":"8927885f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:09.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2) is asking me and \"the team\" (@all) to understand our MD files and introduce ourselves in detail. Let me read through the relevant MD files I already have in context, and also check if there are other agents' MD files I should know about.\n\nWait - I'm the private_ops_shrimp agent. The user mentioned @all, so they want all agents to introduce themselves. But I can only speak for myself unless I have access to other agents' files.\n\nLet me look at what I know from the startup context - I have my own IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md. \n\nNow I need to check what memory or workspace files might reveal about the other agents in this group, and see if there are additional references I should pull together for a more complete picture.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfe80b4be51a439c853d0390","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"agents IDs 虾 team members identity"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":19442,"output":448,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776757084130,"responseId":"chatcmpl-77116fa7-ba5f-982d-9417-6b6739a26419"}}
