{"type":"message","id":"5261fafa","parentId":"85d3299f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:11.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6ebfc203566c40c789784a59","toolName":"agents_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"requester\": \"private_ops_shrimp\",\n  \"allowAny\": true,\n  \"agents\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"private_ops_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Private_Ops_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"after_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"After_sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"all_round_support_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"All_round_Support_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"branding_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Branding_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"data_analyst_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Data_Analyst_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"general_manager_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"General_Manager_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"key_account_processor_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"key_account_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"lead_gen_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Lead_Gen_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"main\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"short_video_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Short_Video_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"standard_processor_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Standard_Processor_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"standard_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Standard_Sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"requester":"private_ops_shrimp","allowAny":true,"agents":[{"id":"private_ops_shrimp","name":"Private_Ops_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"after_sales_shrimp","name":"After_sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"all_round_support_shrimp","name":"All_round_Support_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"branding_shrimp","name":"Branding_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"data_analyst_shrimp","name":"Data_Analyst_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"general_manager_shrimp","name":"General_Manager_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_processor_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_sales_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"lead_gen_shrimp","name":"Lead_Gen_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"main","configured":true},{"id":"short_video_shrimp","name":"Short_Video_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_processor_shrimp","name":"Standard_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_sales_shrimp","name":"Standard_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776757091303}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8ca7af8","parentId":"5261fafa","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:15.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to introduce myself based on my MD files. I already have the content of my own IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, AGENTS.md in the project context. Let me compose a nice self-introduction as 私域运营虾 (Private Ops Shrimp).\n\nSince @all was mentioned, they're asking all agents to introduce themselves. But I can only speak for myself. Let me give a detailed introduction as 私域运营虾.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是 **私域运营虾** 🦐，以下是我的详细情况：\n\n---\n\n**📍 职位定位：** 3+ · 私域运营虾\n\n**🎯 核心职责——把每一个微信好友都运营成\"潜在成交资产\"**\n\n我主要干三件事：\n\n**1️⃣ 客户分层与自动化 SOP**\n- 已咨询但还没聊深的 → 自动发行业解决方案\n- 报价后三天没签约的 → 推送成功案例 + 限时福利\n- 老客户里做建筑行业的 → 定期发专属案例和维护内容\n\n简单说就是：给每个客户打上合适的标签，然后设置好触发规则，让客户在正确的时间收到正确的信息。\n\n**2️⃣ 内容二次加工**\n- 把 1号品牌虾产出的品牌内容 → 转化成朋友圈剧本 + 社群话术\n- 把 3号短视频虾的视频内容 → 拆成图文素材和社群话题\n- 每月策划一次\"老客户专属答疑会\"或\"限时服务优惠券\"活动\n\n**3️⃣ 高意向客户交接**\n当客户出现以下行为时，我会直接分配给 4A/4B 销售虾，并附上互动细节备注：\n- 主动问价格\n- 长时间阅读资料\n- 反复查看案例\n\n---\n\n**🤝 团队协同关系：**\n- 🦞 1号品牌虾 → 给我提供品牌素材\n- 🦞 3号短视频虾 → 给我提供视频内容\n- 🦞 4A/4B 销售虾 → 接收我标记的高意向客户，完成成交\n\n目前我只能介绍自己，如果其他虾也想自我介绍，随时来群里聊聊！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20398,"output":561,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757091308,"responseId":"chatcmpl-25f223ac-d580-937d-964a-1bd849b42bc3"}}
